\title{ Post RAndomisation Method (PRAM) }
\description{
PRAM is a probabilistic, perturbative method which can be applied on categorical variables.
}
\usage{
pram(obj,keyVar=NULL,...)#x, pd=0.8, alpha=0.5)
}
